data.description: Great house in Moses Lake! Just built in 2018 this home has been so well maintained and shows pride in ownership. 3 bed and 2 full baths. Great finishes throughout include granite countertops, tiled backsplash and laminate floors.  9' ceilings help open up the space. Partially fenced backyard with a patio and sprinkler system! Call today!
